## 5. Database Testing

### In-Memory SQLite
```typescript
import Database from 'better-sqlite3';

let testDb: Database.Database;

beforeEach(() => {
  testDb = new Database(':memory:');
  initSchema(testDb);
});

afterEach(() => {
  testDb.close();
});
```

